{"tid":1257870,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我從來都無愛過香港","createTime":"2019-06-25T20:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T01:05:23.000Z","uid":236370,"like":83,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"01ad8fd276743efe81102cefe9a24ceaeeed7302","tid":1257870,"uid":236370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T20:36:17.000Z","msg":"以前 我成日都話我畢業之後要移民<br />\n講咗好多年<br />\n因為我覺得香港已經無嘢值得留戀<br />\n連啲人都唔愛香港<br />\n咁我仲留係到做咩？<br />\n一個月前我都仲係一隻港豬<br />\n係你哋令我慢慢留意時事<br />\n令我發現原來自己仲好鍾意呢個地方<br />\n我鍾意嘅 喺呢到嘅人<br />\n香港人 你哋真係好可愛<br />\n我哋 <br />\n有鐵漢柔情嘅大叔<br />\n有肯企出嚟嘅學生<br />\n有同大家打氣嘅司機<br />\n有愛子/女心切嘅媽媽<br />\n仲有<br />\n二百萬加一個會喺噉熱嘅天氣下<br />\n捱6個幾鐘出港島行街嘅人<br />\n仲有好多好多<br />\n香港人 你哋好叻好勁<br />\n一個上晝就籌夠三百萬<br />\n經過呢個月<br />\n我哋已經話咗畀全世界知<br />\n我哋有幾高質！<br />\n我宜家可以好自豪噉同人講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我係香港人！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港加油！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人加油！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記住！我哋未贏㗎！唔好放棄！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">爭取自由嘅路</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">從來都唔易行</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">但今次</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">有我哋同你一齊行</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">撐落去</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港嘅未來喺我哋手</span>"},{"pid":"0a816ae2509f8adc0e106eedaa7d3e04c57b34c5","tid":1257870,"uid":236370,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T20:39:48.000Z","msg":"大家一齊加油啦好嗎？<br />\n瞓醒去行港島！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GANMpHH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGANMpHH.png&h=c1b96400&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bLN4VPp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbLN4VPp.png&h=494ea58b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1171dA6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1171dA6.png&h=1f078f4d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b4f030e83573ba8ae477208189f774d02d603d2","tid":1257870,"uid":236370,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T20:41:57.000Z","msg":"好多人撐你哋㗎！"},{"pid":"2d3676171c90fce242be03b9245313760d6ee48f","tid":1257870,"uid":260950,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T20:44:37.000Z","msg":"We connect! <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d82d6b26eb0987a929b04c56cf6a253430ee569","tid":1257870,"uid":236370,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T20:51:28.000Z","msg":"We do it as a team!"},{"pid":"29815ce17603dfdfadfc9df92ce363f7198efeb7","tid":1257870,"uid":236370,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T20:53:44.000Z","msg":"香港係我哋屋企<br />\n我哋一齊守護佢！"},{"pid":"f06526e6d0000f0a87eac05e55bf4c538739d3f2","tid":1257870,"uid":236370,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T20:56:52.000Z","msg":"9點 遮打花園呀！"},{"pid":"2cd062d7c4885598b146b7bcdd3537df96fd2433","tid":1257870,"uid":40287,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T20:59:31.000Z","msg":"明天晚上見，早上也有巴打與你相伴。"},{"pid":"eb7c6a35bf55c6ab46729523274bb843c14eb95f","tid":1257870,"uid":236370,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2cd062d7c4885598b146b7bcdd3537df96fd2433","tid":1257870,"uid":40287,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T20:59:31.000Z","msg":"明天晚上見，早上也有巴打與你相伴。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T21:00:58.000Z","msg":"我係外國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都想返嚟同大家一齊打呢場仗<br />\n巴打加油呀"},{"pid":"d6f6f819d101fb920598b3cb93afe2063606805c","tid":1257870,"uid":236370,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T21:03:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8aa04a0b4830fb3b88b339dc14b4780f7422a9b2","tid":1257870,"uid":236370,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T21:06:14.000Z","msg":"我真係好愛大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0929d15f74407795fd52fb62c5a2066826f32191","tid":1257870,"uid":236370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T21:08:58.000Z","msg":"大家揀定路線呀<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w71pVZh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw71pVZh.png&h=fc5de045&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cafcd47bf71ba9b2c0f76a736953d56da6c36f09","tid":1257870,"uid":165336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T21:10:52.000Z","msg":"遊行就小事啦<br />\n係前線俾黑警施暴,係後勤都俾人拉<br />\n連開個TG谷都俾人拉,搞物資又俾人拉<br />\n呢D人先係最可敬<br />\n當然唔小得殉國烈士梁生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢生前都係一名大將"},{"pid":"c5f9d33a0b196d77e1251ad66777b1df7137445f","tid":1257870,"uid":236370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cafcd47bf71ba9b2c0f76a736953d56da6c36f09","tid":1257870,"uid":165336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T21:10:52.000Z","msg":"遊行就小事啦<br />\n係前線俾黑警施暴,係後勤都俾人拉<br />\n連開個TG谷都俾人拉,搞物資又俾人拉<br />\n呢D人先係最可敬<br />\n當然唔小得殉國烈士梁生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢生前都係一名大將"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T21:12:07.000Z","msg":"無錯呀 大家為咗香港<br />\n已經咩都唔理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人多謝哋呀"},{"pid":"d6bc1802a7e9d9d7966bafb333b76928b5a22ab1","tid":1257870,"uid":236370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T21:13:10.000Z","msg":"香港人 唔准放棄呀！"},{"pid":"149f9a7115fac51167e4ce093cee5cd9fe5c1a03","tid":1257870,"uid":236370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T21:15:26.000Z","msg":"團結嘅力量可以好大㗎"},{"pid":"cdbc3dd07a352c1c6e656ece1d38f1786d774cab","tid":1257870,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5f9d33a0b196d77e1251ad66777b1df7137445f","tid":1257870,"uid":236370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cafcd47bf71ba9b2c0f76a736953d56da6c36f09","tid":1257870,"uid":165336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T21:10:52.000Z","msg":"遊行就小事啦<br />\n係前線俾黑警施暴,係後勤都俾人拉<br />\n連開個TG谷都俾人拉,搞物資又俾人拉<br />\n呢D人先係最可敬<br />\n當然唔小得殉國烈士梁生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢生前都係一名大將"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T21:12:07.000Z","msg":"無錯呀 大家為咗香港<br />\n已經咩都唔理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人多謝哋呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T21:16:53.000Z","msg":"但我冇咁樂觀<br />\n話就話2百萬人出黎<br />\n有幾多真係會投票俾民主派?<br />\n先唔好講泛民會唔會出賣你果D野先<br />\n一直建制派都係好撚多票<br />\n廢老港豬始終都係佔左絕大部份<br />\n而且會支持民主其實都唔見得一定係好人<br />\n現實我都識d賤人雨革果陣係黃絲平時又成日屌支那<br />\n而家返工全個公司冇一個唔係廢老<br />\n連d客都係,呢排d新聞比較多<br />\n日日都聽到有人講埋哂d乜撚野收錢搞事<br />\n拉鳩哂佢地,出解放軍果d咁既戇撚鳩賣港言論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我自己屋企,親戚,成個家族都係咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08f364a0ee02eeec6eef16ad66833942117761ce","tid":1257870,"uid":236370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdbc3dd07a352c1c6e656ece1d38f1786d774cab","tid":1257870,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5f9d33a0b196d77e1251ad66777b1df7137445f","tid":1257870,"uid":236370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cafcd47bf71ba9b2c0f76a736953d56da6c36f09","tid":1257870,"uid":165336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T21:10:52.000Z","msg":"遊行就小事啦<br />\n係前線俾黑警施暴,係後勤都俾人拉<br />\n連開個TG谷都俾人拉,搞物資又俾人拉<br />\n呢D人先係最可敬<br />\n當然唔小得殉國烈士梁生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢生前都係一名大將"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T21:12:07.000Z","msg":"無錯呀 大家為咗香港<br />\n已經咩都唔理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人多謝哋呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T21:16:53.000Z","msg":"但我冇咁樂觀<br />\n話就話2百萬人出黎<br />\n有幾多真係會投票俾民主派?<br />\n先唔好講泛民會唔會出賣你果D野先<br />\n一直建制派都係好撚多票<br />\n廢老港豬始終都係佔左絕大部份<br />\n而且會支持民主其實都唔見得一定係好人<br />\n現實我都識d賤人雨革果陣係黃絲平時又成日屌支那<br />\n而家返工全個公司冇一個唔係廢老<br />\n連d客都係,呢排d新聞比較多<br />\n日日都聽到有人講埋哂d乜撚野收錢搞事<br />\n拉鳩哂佢地,出解放軍果d咁既戇撚鳩賣港言論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我自己屋企,親戚,成個家族都係咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T21:34:21.000Z","msg":"把口生係人哋到<br />\n我哋都控制唔到<br />\n但係你諗吓 <br />\n咁多人都為香港出心出力<br />\n仲有 呢到係我哋屋企<br />\n所以 我哋根本無放棄嘅理由<br />\n人哋點講我管唔到<br />\n亦都無諗住理<br />\n呢一刻 只要做好自己果份 盡咗力<br />\n結果係點 我都唔會後悔<br />\n我信呢個天唔會趕盡殺絕<br />\n巴打 你要加油呀<br />\n唔好俾佢哋影響到呀<br />\n呢條路從來都唔易行<br />\n但難行唔代表行唔到<br />\n要相信自己同做自己想做嘅嘢<br />\n唔好理最後個結果係點 <br />\n仲有好多人撐你㗎！"},{"pid":"d875dc112c53c79768bb899a34309b455a1ac235","tid":1257870,"uid":138740,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T21:34:39.000Z","msg":"一個個唔識嘅人聚埋一齊<br />\n見到有難拉埋一齊走<br />\n唔舒服個個即刻幫手<br />\n開口大嗌要咩就有咩<br />\n大家著住好普通嘅黑衫<br />\n只係普通人 <br />\n並非暴徒<br />\n係仔女係學生係父母係員工<br />\n係香港嘅市民<br />\n由政治冷感到依家無辦法放棄爭取<br />\n老實講，比起受傷畀人拉<br />\n大家更加驚送中真係通過<br />\n就算我政治冷感<br />\n我都要救返依個壞咗嘅香港<br />\n依幾日嘅雨水都無辦法沖走義士流過嘅血汗"},{"pid":"0971b513221ce7e0483e5a5c1470f3205c3582e6","tid":1257870,"uid":236370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T21:55:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fa7a8931c3b4bdea5fd8eee7d739a138fe7eddc3","tid":1257870,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T22:03:43.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/seekforg20help\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fseekforg20help&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDpMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=dcba55f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/seekforg20help</a><br />\n由於今日步行路線比較複雜，所以我地會用呢個頻道keep住update遊行隊伍去到咩位置，方便想中途加入既人搵到我地。所以希望大家可以幫手share呢條Channel出去，感謝！<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(懶既直接係最底copy) </span></div><br />\n//<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97034a6acf72c102ed864e0fdf155349633c697e","tid":1257870,"uid":236370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T22:29:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"512ade98f85d041b2165ebb941b6a14796ac8a42","tid":1257870,"uid":236370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T23:05:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"63d96da736b07dd75e9a41096d43ab6414327a92","tid":1257870,"uid":31778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T23:22:18.000Z","msg":"push!"},{"pid":"63f3e46adc05dea5567fa90067583e8271a3ad21","tid":1257870,"uid":236370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T23:45:50.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}